articles.title: NASA Uncovers Life’s Building Blocks in Asteroid Bennu’s Pristine Sample - SciTechDaily
articles.description: NASA’s OSIRIS-REx mission delivered samples from asteroid Bennu, revealing crucial molecules linked to life, including amino acids and nucleobases found in DNA and RNA. The presence of ammonia and formaldehyde suggests conditions ripe for forming complex mole…
